":"dac9b8b38cdd14afb357e0d594df6c3ac61ab441","tid":21754,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到一半無睇 <br />\n應該係領養完又棄養 搵spca 殺左隻狗<br />\n<br />\n根本義工啲準則咁煩鳩咪又係阻唔到啲仆街領養</blockquote><br />\n係 相反有d真心對d狗好既又比班人彈三彈四 又話屋細又呢樣果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 好難界定邊啲養得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又話你未夠25歲<br />\n又話你收入未夠3萬<br />\n又話你個樣似虐狗<br />\n有話你唔係屬貓 唔養得貓。<br />\n<br />\n根本係離曬譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33adc043a824fb1c414f67f7bef3c849a5de828","tid":21754,"uid":9873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7781f87f06d41b798ea0e38ef3114f697d7ed77a","tid":21754,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到一半無睇 <br />\n應該係領養完又棄養 搵spca 殺左隻狗<br />\n<br />\n根本義工啲準則咁煩鳩咪又係阻唔到啲仆街領養</blockquote><br />\n係 相反有d真心對d狗好既又比班人彈三彈四 又話屋細又呢樣果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 好難界定邊啲養得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又話你未夠25歲<br />\n又話你收入未夠3萬<br />\n又話你個樣似虐狗<br />\n有話你唔係屬貓 唔養得貓。<br />\n<br />\n根本係離曬譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n義工既準則係咩？ <br />\n大部分都係見人中產有錢、住私樓間屋好大、身光頸靚，咪有能力有條件領養囉，即刻狗沖送4隻狗比人，間接害死4隻狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係寒酸窮公屋仔，就算講明公屋係可以養貓，查你九百幾樣野，到最後都係話覺得你唔適合，連養隻貓仔都唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ade5d6ecca77e3ee770f561b4821def7be9d66","tid":21754,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到一半無睇 <br />\n應該係領養完又棄養 搵spca 殺左隻狗<br />\n<br />\n根本義工啲準則咁煩鳩咪又係阻唔到啲仆街領養</blockquote><br />\n係 相反有d真心對d狗好既又比班人彈三彈四 又話屋細又呢樣果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 好難界定邊啲養得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又話你未夠25歲<br />\n又話你收入未夠3萬<br />\n又話你個樣似虐狗<br />\n有話你唔係屬貓 唔養得貓。<br />\n<br />\n根本係離曬譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n義工既準則係咩？ <br />\n大部分都係見人中產有錢、住私樓間屋好大、身光頸靚，咪有能力有條件領養囉，即刻狗沖送4隻狗比人，間接害死4隻狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係寒酸窮公屋仔，就算講明公屋係可以養貓，查你九百幾樣野，到最後都係話覺得你唔適合，連養隻貓仔都唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇個義工寫個啲咩人地住兩層村屋，居住環境理想乜乜乜，就知啦。原來判斷人地適唔適合領養就係睇人有無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba7f0d559a8e2187d801fb62f7b3c6398ad6a31","tid":21754,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為免比人拎上黎公審，大家比多少少錢去舖頭買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後你再拎去愛協都無問題</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">或者夏至拎去玉林</span>"},{"pid":"8c27108965230af04e856a30cc96314245aca022","tid":21754,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bl